      <tr><td>Rheumatoid arthritis</td><td>Warm paraffin bath (hands). Tepid neutral bath during flare.</td><td>Gentle stretching in remission. Yoga Nidra for pain.</td><td>Fish oil EPA 3–6g ★, Curcumin 1g BD, Probiotics VSL#3, Vit D3 4000IU, Folate (if on MTX).</td></tr>
